" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩可以問 盡量答<br />\n不過呢啲唔係個個 work<br />\n試下冇壞 反正大家應該都絕望到乜撚野都試"},{"pid":"5c53b178d8973b9849ed311f80c4baa436b39870","tid":9621,"uid":287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"盡量食清啲<br />\n我食左二個禮拜接近素食 冇再痕<br />\n係啲印好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d38f1fae5d54b3f1c85bed691f9c99b5bc816cf","tid":9621,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇中醫+針灸 真係有用<br />\n我舊年狂爆 全身都係 三個月好番九成<br />\n而家間唔中都會痕 但唔會惡化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我女朋友睇完中醫仲嚴重左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初頭我都會，但之後會慢慢退晒<br />\n如果之前搽過類固醇既話，初頭係會發晒出黎"},{"pid":"a52071260fa2997f33291f0e218faf6fad59fc14","tid":9621,"uid":6767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算濕疹 但一到冬天好多位都會好痕忍唔住r<br />\n留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf26149efa9fd465823ca1c5fd2b02ce7a89234","tid":9621,"uid":17834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"等我試下食清啲！試下素食一排會唔會好啲先"},{"pid":"d910175dd60bce6163b23372a91d801dac829451","tid":9621,"uid":17834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要呻下！最近啲濕疹勁翻 翻學啲野多到做唔哂咁制 有壓力之餘又訓得少 啱啱仲要訓得個3個中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痕到仆街 <br />\n極度懷疑我係壓力先有濕疹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得絕對有關係呀 所以要保持正面思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係負面撚 尤其係夜晚沖完涼 熄燈上床開始痕嘅時候就會跌落深坑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41283927290b2e4d00bda608c1b44165d5fe1bca","tid":9621,"uid":18559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"15年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5affc9c93072a2dbbaab